snippet.title: Frank Stephenson
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official channel of world-renowned designer; Frank Stephenson. Here you will find exclusive content that dives deep into the wonderful world of Frank's creativity, talking you through his thoughts on design philospophy, sharing wisdom concerning curiosity and the creative pursuit gained from over 35 years as a designer & giving his thoughts and reactions to the worlds modern, cutting-edge designs. 
BIO: 'Frank Stephenson is a British-Spanish-American automobile designer widely known for his design work at Mini, Ferrari, Maserati, Fiat, Alfa Romeo, and McLaren.

Artwork Sketches, Colouring Book and T shirts are now in Store at https://www.frankstephenson.com/store 

To watch the 'Chasing Perfect' film documentary, Motor Trend in the USA, available worldwide on all downloads, Amazon, iTunes etc

For business enquiries: www.frankstephensonmedia.com, email: Linda@frankstephenson.com
